id: pm-lwtx
title: 2026-06-02 commander SDK custom-field and extension-output hardening
description: "Fresh broad manual audit and optimization pass requested on 2026-06-02 covering latest pm CLI, SDK, package ecosystem, temp-project dogfood, GitHub reports, dependency update PR #93, issue #96 output override diagnostics, and issue #97 custom field setters. Duplicate check: pm context/list-open/list-in-progress plus targeted search found closed broad-audit lineage pm-59gj, pm-kd9n, pm-etxf, pm-z0ip, pm-kddw and open direct follow-ups pm-qvdj, pm-5teq, pm-kcba; this task tracks this later audit pass and links fixes to the existing direct items rather than creating duplicates."
type: Task
status: in_progress
priority: 0
